{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"33345-minna-tabechatta","title":"みんな たべちゃった！","description":"ジャングルが いつも きれいなのは、なぜ？\r\nそこでは ムダにすてられるものなんて、なにひとつ ないからだよ！","language":"Japanese","langCode":"ja","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sakura Mashio"],"illustrators":["Rohan Chakravarty"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/33345-minna-tabechatta"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/188968/size3/715cc0ac513fbf98008ab8be6fa089d2.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/188968/size6/715cc0ac513fbf98008ab8be6fa089d2.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48918/size6/3f3ac741980cc208e814de67c6869529.jpg","text":"ここジャングルでは、むだに すてられるものなんて、ない。\nな〜んにも、ない！\nあとかたもなく、きれいに なくなっちゃうのさ。\nほんとうの ほんとうに、なんでもさ！","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48919/size6/b58c99034969bc162cef06fd075a954a.jpg","text":"たとえば、ヒョウがたべのこしたら、\nのこったぶんは、だれが たべるとおもう？\nハゲタカと、ハイエナさ！","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48920/size6/a15b1e625ddf40765e8e5c003e3c2b46.jpg","text":"それから、はらをすかせた イノシシだ。\nブヒ、ブヒ、ブヒヒ！","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48921/size6/c114039e78138e4cd6fff550955aa731.jpg","text":"じゃあもし、ハゲタカとハイエナが エサをのこしたら、\nのこりを たいらげるのは だれだ？\nハエと、ウジムシさ！","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48922/size6/e4bc6289abe48e7d9f785620fc530683.jpg","text":"それから、はらをすかせた イノシシだ。\nブヒ、ブヒ、ブヒヒ！","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48931/size6/70c6baabb12b38c961f78078bfe0ccfe.jpg","text":"じゃあさ、ゾウが ふん するだろ。\nそれを おやつがわりに するのは だれだ？\nフンコロガシさ！","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48933/size6/e43a74b0239462bf25802d946640cd5b.jpg","text":"それから、はらをすかした イノシシさ！\nブヒ、ブヒ、ブヒヒ！","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48925/size6/05089a3aefce21a5974a1f8f7b86f839.jpg","text":"きのえだや、はっぱ、じめんにたまった あめのみず。\nこの ごちそうに ありつくのは だれ？\nシロアリと、カビたちさ！","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48926/size6/6712da7ee6bfe2b1ac0912e09764e94a.jpg","text":"それから、はらをすかせた イノシシだ。\nブヒ、ブヒ、ブヒヒ！","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48927/size6/36fefdc2bad5ae460bff3b65d5e0e241.jpg","text":"じゃあ、けむりで くうきがよごれてしまったら、\nそれを みんな すいこんでしまうのは だれ？\nき だよ！","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48928/size6/126a5ea466b1124b1dc3e09d1b8bb663.jpg","text":"はらをすかせた イノシシは およびじゃないぜ。\nブヒ、ブヒ、ブヒヒ！","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":56}}